[0.002, "o", " running httpd, as with most system services.\u001b[K\r\u001b[34d#\u001b[K\u001b[35d\bUser http\u001b[K\r\u001b[36dGroup http\u001b[K\r\u001b[37d\u001b[K\u001b[38d</IfModule>\u001b[K\r\u001b[39d\u001b[K\u001b[40d# 'Main' server configuration\u001b[K\r\u001b[41d#\u001b[K\u001b[42d"]
[0.001, "o", " The directives in this section set up the values used by the 'main'\r\u001b[43d# server, which responds to any requests that aren't handled by a\r\u001b[44d# <VirtualHost> definition.  These values also provide defaults for\r\u001b[45d# any <VirtualHost> containers you may define later in the file.\r\u001b[24d#"]
